Release milestones occur at roughly 6 week intervals and follow the Platform milestone releases by approximately 2 weeks; 
that is, until the final 3.7 release of the Platform, upon which GMF Tooling and other projects will release simultaneously. 
It is anticipated that GMF Tooling will synchronize its release milestones with the Juno release schedule for +3 components.
